-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Third-party components
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This project does not bundle any third-party JavaScript libraries or runtime
dependencies. All Node.js code uses only built-in modules (http, https, fs,
path). The browser-based dashboard is a single-file SPA with no external
script or stylesheet dependencies.

Infrastructure dependencies pulled at runtime (not bundled):

  nginx (Alpine Linux variant)
    License : BSD 2-Clause "Simplified" License
    Source  : https://nginx.org / https://hub.docker.com/_/nginx

  Node.js (Alpine Linux variant)
    License : MIT License (Node.js core), various (bundled V8/libuv/etc.)
    Source  : https://nodejs.org / https://hub.docker.com/_/node

  Alpine Linux
    License : Various (GPL, MIT, etc.) — see https://alpinelinux.org
    Source  : https://alpinelinux.org

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
OWASP Dependency-Track
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This dashboard is a read-only UI layer that connects to an existing
OWASP Dependency-Track instance. Dependency-Track itself is not bundled
with or distributed as part of this project.

